<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="single-adj">single <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'sɪŋɡl/    美 /'sɪŋɡl/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>单个的；单一的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>every single</strong> detail of the incident
这次事件的每个细节</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a single survivor
唯一的幸存者</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>单人 (用) 的；单程的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a single room / bed
单人间/床</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a single ticket
单程票</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>未婚的；单身的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a single man
单身男士</p></div></div>